column3: For the years ended June 30, 2023 (“fiscal 2023”), June 30, 2022 (“fiscal 2022”), and June 30, 2021 (“fiscal 2021”), Professional Employer Organization (“PEO”) revenues are net of direct pass-through costs, primarily consisting of payroll wages and payroll taxes, of $66,731.7 million, $62,619.2 million, and $51,362.3 million, respectively.
